<plot>A crook, his moll, and his dimwitted brother set about stealing a valuable jewel during a high-society party. They impersonate a trio of musicians hired to play for the affair, and when the real musicians show up, the gang must not only convince the party-goers that they can play the instruments, they must also persuade the partiers that the real musicians are crooks out to steal the jewel.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?598052</url></doc>
